				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Lu%E1%BA%ADn-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-29/poem-J0hldydC0mlN88NxKv8Y7A">Luận thi kỳ 29 - 論詩其二十九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c/poem-EpzWfGVBH2wEhP3RsbFZjA">Thanh bình nhạc - 清平樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/author-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Hạ Chú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-th%E1%BB%8B-lang/poem-kKKya_32gaAAKOjlLu0ISA">Tống Lưu thị lang - 送劉侍郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/author-vHSGJ24Oq83oesxet8BFJA">Lý Đoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Tr%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m-t%E1%BB%B1-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Mc4k6zFtMVVoCTp1K6yCxw">Trúc Lâm tự biệt hữu nhân - 竹林寺別友人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Vi%C3%AAm/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-o%C3%A1n-C%E1%BB%B1u-c%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-j-_jcR-6X5MnT2edQjnRog">Trường đình oán - Cựu cư hữu cảm - 長亭怨－舊居有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Vi%C3%AAm/author-M_XPpOUpF8GZqWE9vo6bVg">Trương Viêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-NNj51-ebZyApj8ndjN6_VQ">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-hoan-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-3PYyCjUyU4U_6BATabSldA">Tương kiến hoan kỳ 1 - 相見歡其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/V%E1%BB%8B-th%C3%AA-t%C3%A1c-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%C3%BD-%C3%BD/poem-kODCpGEfWjo_G2eysclnHQ">Vị thê tác sinh nhật ký ý - 為妻作生日寄意</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/author-FLeQSz8PiNWt7aZh3N_djw">Lý Dĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Phu-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-bmEpQKC5Snm4e9GWOHc3nA">Vọng Phu thạch - 望夫石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
